What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Kids Tablet Market?

Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Kids Tablet Market

Kids tablet market is expected to gain market growth in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Data Bridge Market Research analyses the kids tablet market to reach at an estimated value of USD 28,101.2 million by 2028 and exhibit a CAGR of 14.10% for the forecast period of 2021-2028.

Kids tablet refers to a small handheld device with touchscreen technology consisting of various different software applications used by the kids especially for educating or gaming purposes. They use have wireless internet or local area networks. The kid tablets helps in the development of an aptitude for technology, learn and stimulate the mind and assists in promoting cognitive and social development of the kid.

The increasing adoption of the BYOD concept in modern schools across the globe will emerge as the major factor driving market growth. The high preference by parents for game-based learning, rapid increase in online learning and awareness regarding its benefits such as the development of vital skills will further aggravate the market value. However, rising demand for smartphones among kids, concerns regarding the health of kids and child identity, and less memory than laptops act as a restraint for the market.

In addition to this, rising technological advancements such as various design features like impact-proof tablet body to withstand thrashing, rounded corners, scratch-resistant screen, and rising level of internet penetration create new opportunities for growing the market within the forecast period. The decline in the sales of various devices including the tablets owing to the COVID-19 pandemic which led to slowdown in the manufacturing sector will dampen the growth rate that further result as a challenge for the market.

